{"name": "odoo-addon-l10n-ro-config", "metadata": {"name": "odoo-addon-l10n-ro-config", "version": "18.0.0.2.0", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 6 - Mature", "Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 18.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/l10n-romania", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo"], "summary": "Romania - Localization Install and Config Applications", "upload_time": 1731409451}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Mature-brightgreen.png\n    :alt: Mature\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fl10n--romania-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/l10n-romania\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/l10n-romania/tree/18.0/l10n_ro_config\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/l10n-romania-18-0/l10n-romania-18-0-l10n_ro_config\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/l10n-romania&target_branch=18.0\n    ```\n  maintainer-feketemihai: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/feketemihai.png?size=40px\n    :alt: feketemihai\n    :target: https://github.com/feketemihai\n    ```\n---\n\n# Romania - Localization Config\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:0f1434d652f90d9b07eead87e66e41b62406f5c0423e6d2199a78ef40bbb00f5\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module allows you to install and configure all the localization\nmodules related to Romania. Some of the modules will load data at\ninstall.\n\nFor Romanian companies, you will have a dedicated page in Configuration,\nfrom where you cna install rest of the modules, or set up some added\nfields for localization.\n\n\\* All changes added by the Romanian localization will only apply for\ncompanies that have the \"Use Romanian Accounting\" checkbox set.\n\n\\* All menus and fields are visible in the interface if you are working\non a Romanian company, otherwise the are hidden.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Installation\n\nTo install this module, you need to:\n\n- clone the branch 14.0 of the repository\n  <https://github.com/OCA/l10n-romania>\n- add the path to this repository in your configuration (addons-path)\n- update the module list\n- search for \"Romania - Localization Config\" in your addons\n- install the module\n\n## Usage\n\n### Companies\n\n- You can complete dedicated fields for Romanian companies, like \"Share\n  Capital\", \"CAEN Code\".\n- From Romanian page from Configuration, you can define new properties\n  for your company, depending on the modules that you have installed.\n\n### Partners\n\n- You can complete dedicated fields for Romanian partners, like \"VAT\n  Subjected\", \"CAEN Code\", \"E-invoicing\".\n- You can input also partners without VAT country code, but you need to\n  select also the country.\n\n### Products\n\n- Use different taxes for \"Service\" products, they are defined in the\n  Chart of Accounts, but here we set up the default taxes used.\n\n### Bank Accounts\n\n- Tick the \"Ro Print in Report\" fields if you want the bank account to\n  be printed in reports (not all reports are updated but you can use\n  the example from the Invoice Report to change the other report where\n  you want to print the bank accounts).\n\n  \\*\\* This applies also for company bank accounts, there you can use\n  also the related field from Account Journal to mark them.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-romania/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-romania/issues/new?body=module:%20l10n_ro_config%0Aversion:%2018.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- NextERP Romania\n- Forest and Biomass Romania\n\n### Contributors\n\n- [NextERP Romania](https://www.nexterp.ro):\n\n  - Fekete Mihai \\<<mailto:feketemihai@nexterp.ro>>\n\n- [Terrabit](https://www.terrabit.ro):\n\n  - Dorin Hongu \\<<mailto:dhongu@gmail.com>>\n\n- Adrian Vasile \\<<mailto:adrian.vasile@gmail.com>>\n\n- [QDev Web Labs](https://qdev.ro):\n\n  - Anastasescu R\u0103zvan-Ioan \\<<mailto:razvan@qdev.ro>>\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with\ntechnical issues.\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nCurrent [maintainer](https://odoo-community.org/page/maintainer-role):\n\n{{ maintainer-feketemihai }}\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/l10n-romania](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-romania/tree/18.0/l10n_ro_config) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_config.wizard", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_config.wizard.res_config_settings", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_config.wizard..res_config_settings", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_config.models.res_bank", "documentation": ["Copyright 2018 NextERP Romania", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl.html)"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_config.models.res_bank.ResPartnerBank", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_config.models.res_bank.ResPartnerBank._name", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_config.models.res_bank.ResPartnerBank._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_config.models.res_bank.ResPartnerBank.l10n_ro_print_report", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_config.models.l10n_ro_mixin", "documentation": ["Copyright 2022 NextERP Romania", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl.html)"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_config.models.l10n_ro_mixin.L10nRoMixin", "bases": ["models.AbstractModel"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_config.models.l10n_ro_mixin.L10nRoMixin._compute_is_l10n_ro_record", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_ro_config.models.l10n_ro_mixin.L10nRoMixin._check_company_id_in_fields", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type":